t anim id est laborum.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Blockquotes</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Single line blockquote:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Multi line blockquote with a cite reference:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</p><p>Will Smooth  Orange Worldwide Developers Conference, 2018</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.\n</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.\n</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Tables</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><thead><tr><th>Employee</th><th>Salary</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><th><a href=\"http://example.org/\">John Doe</a></th><td>$1</td><td>Because thats all Steve Jobs needed for a salary.</td></tr><tr><th><a href=\"http://example.org/\">Jane Doe</a></th><td>$100K</td><td>For all the blogging she does.</td></tr><tr><th><a href=\"http://example.org/\">Fred Bloggs</a></th><td>$100M</td><td>Pictures are worth a thousand words, right? So Jane x 1,000.</td></tr><tr><th><a href=\"http://example.org/\">Jane Bloggs</a></th><td>$100B</td><td>With hair like that?! Enough said</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Definition Lists</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nDefinition List Title\nDefinition list division.\nStartup\nA startup company or startup is a company or temporary organization designed to search for a repeatable and scalable business model.\n#dowork\nCoined by Rob Dyrdek and his personal body guard Christopher Big Black Boykins, Do Work works as a self motivator, to motivating your friends.\nDo It Live\nIll let Bill OReilly will <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_HyZ5aW76c\">explain</a> this one.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Unordered List (Nested)</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>List item one\n<ul><li>List item one\n<ul><li>List item one</li><li>List item two</li><li>List item three</li><li>List item four</li></ul>\n</li><li>List item two</li><li>List item three</li><li>List item four</li></ul>\n</li><li>List item two</li><li>List item three</li><li>List item four</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Ordered List</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>List item one\n<ol><li>List item one\n<ol><li>List item one</li><li>List item two</li><li>List item three</li><li>List item four</li></ol>\n</li><li>List item two</li><li>List item three</li><li>List item four</li></ol>\n</li><li>List item two</li><li>List item three</li><li>List item four</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Mixed List (Nested)</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Unordered list item one</li><li>Unordered list item two\n<ol><li>Ordered list item one</li><li>Ordered list item two\n<ul><li>Unordered list item one</li><li>Unordered list item two\n<ol><li>Ordered list item one</li><li>Ordered list item two</li><li>Ordered list item three</li></ol>\n</li><li>Unordered list item three</li></ul>\n</li><li>Ordered list item three</li></ol>\n</li><li>Unordered list item three</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML Tags</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These supported tags come from the WordPress.com code <a href=\"http://en.support.wordpress.com/code/\">FAQ</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Address Tag</strong>\n1 Infinite Loop<br>Cupertino, CA 95014<br>United States\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Anchor Tag (aka. Link)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example of a <a href=\"http://apple.com\">link</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Abbreviation Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The abbreviation <abbr title=\"Seriously\">srsly</abbr> stands for seriously.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Acronym Tag (<em>deprecated in HTML5</em>)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The acronym ftw stands for for the win.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Big Tag (<em>deprecated in HTML5</em>)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These tests are a big deal, but this tag is no longer supported in HTML5.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Cite Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Code is poetry. Automattic</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Code Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><code>Code tag test</code></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You will learn later on in these tests that <code>word-wrap: break-word;</code> will be your best friend.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Delete Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This tag will let you <del>strikeout text</del>, but this tag is no longer supported in HTML5 (use the <code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> instead).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Emphasize Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The emphasize tag should <em>italicize</em> text.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Insert Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This tag should denote <ins>inserted</ins> text.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Keyboard Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This scarsly known tag emulates keyboard text, which is usually styled like the <code>&lt;code&gt;</code> tag.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Preformatted Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This tag styles large blocks of code.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">.post-title {\n								margin: 0 0 5px;\n								font-weight: bold;\n								font-size: 38px;\n								line-height: 1.2;\n								and here\'s a line of some really, really, really, really long text, just to see how the PRE tag handles it and to find out how it overflows;\n							}</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Quote Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Developers, developers, developers Steve Ballmer</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Strike Tag (<em>deprecated in HTML5</em>)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This tag shows strike-through text</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Strong Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This tag shows <strong>bold text.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Subscript Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Getting our science styling on with H<sub>2</sub>O, which should push the 2 down.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Superscript Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Still sticking with science and Isaac Newtons E = MC<sup>2</sup>, which should lift the 2 up.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Teletype Tag (<em>deprecated in HTML5</em>)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This rarely used tag emulates teletype text, which is usually styled like the <code>&lt;code&gt;</code> tag.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Variable Tag</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This allows you to denote variables.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2019-04-12 10:08:00', '2019-04-12 10:08:00', '', 0, 'https://demo.themespiral.com/freenews/?page_id=162', 0, 'page', '', 0),
